### Linux-specific bashrc

# 'ls -Gphaltr' only works on Mac OSX, we need to do this
# to get color
# https://askubuntu.com/questions/16336/how-to-get-coloured-terminal-over-ssh
# https://superuser.com/questions/183876/how-do-i-get-ls-color-auto-to-work-on-mac-os-x
alias l="ls -Gphaltr --color=auto"
